<li>[ ] Create an <code>llms.txt</code> file that maps your site structure for AI systems</li>
<li>[ ] Ensure your <code>robots.txt</code> allows AI crawlers (GPTBot, ClaudeBot, PerplexityBot). Read our <a href="/blog/ai-crawlers-guide/">AI crawlers guide</a> for details.</li>
<li>[ ] Improve page speed. Agents time out on slow pages just like users bounce.</li>
<li>[ ] Fix all broken links and redirect chains. Agents follow links programmatically.</li>
</ul>
